{"tid":1559243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港三隻色。黃，綠，藍。","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:46:59.000Z","uid":282768,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79779e30323537a7cddbe802f8107feac5a36df8","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"今時今日，事情發展到宜個地步。<br />\n<br />\n香港已經成功分裂成三派人：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗多講，當然係支持反送中，覺得黑警，港政府好有問題。 同埋好熱愛香港既港人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span> ： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍色無分深淺，都係覺得示威者搞事， 破壞。係搗亂社會既分化者，相信大部分人身邊都有唔小，重點都係支持林鄭政府同埋黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span> ： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到今時今日，咁多人被捕，受傷，經過721，831，都可以話自己中立兩邊都唔幫唔支持既人。 發現綠色既人都好驚得罪其中一邊或者仲係抱住睇定啲既心態。想成為最終利益既得者，唔排除有部分係新聞唔睇唔理世事既人。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有感而發，今日仲聽到有人話自己中立兩邊都唔幫。 我真係想講一句 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你食屎啦</span></span>。睇下新聞，了解下成件事，問下自己良心，訓醒啦香港人。<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999.... 最後，<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce5e3607ffefe479444d3f681b67fea68e886df","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a531e9042e997cbd4dcdc724904119cdc3a52dc2","tid":1559243,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"75476ada0887aae3d2611ec0638e65a23285ef9b","tid":1559243,"uid":86828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"地獄裏最熾熱之處，是留給那些在出現重大道德危機時，保持中立的人<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">但丁</div>"},{"pid":"f360581c205ed2b73d878e75371a7a6be4857ede","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bf818821791b9a753366ff00a492abc9bb3154c8","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"0d483b845a54b2b5cf508b532ee77e721527b464","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"6c2fac2c97da71086bb2b6efcbe8d072e3394b1d","tid":1559243,"uid":282768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"c0b5534746eab807c5999e4bc2bb0297a8c9ff74","tid":1559243,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"巴打建議你唔洗咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n我之前都有同樣嘅諗法<br />\n最後睇左呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6g4QOGqMBY&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRei1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=26da1e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY</a><br />\n有d長但要睇哂<br />\n<br />\n社會上最多嘅一定係騎牆<br />\n要動搖佢地<br />\n就係要令佢地清楚知道邊面就贏<br />\n咁佢地就會好似勝利球迷咁支持你<br />\n<br />\n你對佢地不抱有希望<br />\n就唔會有失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e6463679